text: Anne Lolk Thomsen (born 15 May 1983) is a Danish rower. She competed in the women's lightweight double sculls event at the 2016 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Danish female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Denmark Category:Rowers at the 2012 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
